{"tid":1935553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌夠留學生？","createTime":"2020-03-20T15:53:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T17:58:13.000Z","uid":263389,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"332f32a1ccfa526f800453c2731bde677c0952e5","tid":1935553,"uid":263389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T15:53:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>首先</strong> <br />\n抗爭時有幾多留學生幫手搞遊行搞海外文宣？<br />\n個陣就日日叫留學生幫手乜乜乜<br />\n包括香港買唔到豬嘴 叫留學生寄返黎香港<br />\n起碼我識嘅留學生都係全深黃<br />\n而唔係你地口中高高在上不聞不問嘅人<br />\n(唔排除有呢啲人 但我唔希望大家一竹竿打一船人)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>其次</strong><br />\n你地話留學生係自私撚<br />\n咁點解你地係香港買唔到口罩個陣<br />\n又飛日本韓國掃曬人地啲口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地咁樣又做得好好？你地個陣就唔自私？<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">只許州官放火不許百姓點燈？</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>再者</strong><br />\n留學生 (美加英澳紐) 屋企都絕對唔係基層<br />\n基本上都係<span style=\"color: red;\">中產</span> 或中上階層<br />\n咁如果留學生父母一年交緊幾十萬税<br />\n而佢又持有香港passport <br />\n咁點解佢地個仔就唔可以享有醫療福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而你班基層交得個少少就可以？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><ins>點解唔屌家居隔離14日偷走出嚟嗰啲<br />\n點解唔屌仲係咁去旅行個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></ins></span><br />\n留學生此時此刻可能都好不知所措<br />\n人地可能都只係想有咩事 有屋企人係身邊"},{"pid":"55b7a79bd4985f7f171ffcb9dd5be2e299d3b5f7","tid":1935553,"uid":67425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"上連登唔好認真<br />\n因為好多正常人都唔上連登 何況comment"},{"pid":"a57e3d3f9f99d604db23f11ece0adab3d7583900","tid":1935553,"uid":67425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91e68b34d4c3e5181a8a3c8cede1ac7f87a210ae","tid":1935553,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7bf8539998c2ff386d8a545e17edd6b80227d0","tid":1935553,"uid":74303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"偷走自私西嘅 ig：purdee_luk<br />\n屌啦"},{"pid":"e4d7077560cb8c1e230b22af0c90be6af7654352","tid":1935553,"uid":296119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"留學生而家做錯係咪唔可以屌<br />\n係疫區返黎又唔知有冇病<br />\n就算唔係強制<br />\n自己都好應該隔離14日"},{"pid":"66e99b9c198618d4331924faacfc9321e81ae3d8","tid":1935553,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ba7bf8539998c2ff386d8a545e17edd6b80227d0","tid":1935553,"uid":74303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:03:49.000Z","msg":"偷走自私西嘅 ig：purdee_luk<br />\n屌啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/21/000551_ec1c4592b184bc328d68a03568313543.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F21%2F000551_ec1c4592b184bc328d68a03568313543.png&h=f951874b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/21/000553_0aa8389b69d5b08419189133850f4a4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F21%2F000553_0aa8389b69d5b08419189133850f4a4b.png&h=4d73f8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/03/21/000554_823a6647a93d98f263b9b29e6f33e72e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F03%2F21%2F000554_823a6647a93d98f263b9b29e6f33e72e.png&h=685c2142&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa6a3cd0e08b579c52784225f09325b9fb2c1c60","tid":1935553,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5436a3f3509cf908e65b02148f732c84128bf4a4","tid":1935553,"uid":263389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d7077560cb8c1e230b22af0c90be6af7654352","tid":1935553,"uid":296119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:05:42.000Z","msg":"留學生而家做錯係咪唔可以屌<br />\n係疫區返黎又唔知有冇病<br />\n就算唔係強制<br />\n自己都好應該隔離14日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T16:24:05.000Z","msg":"做錯咪屌 咁冇錯個啲又要屌？"},{"pid":"8cb8728916369d3053f68033258b63b4bbae6387","tid":1935553,"uid":168669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"返黎做咩撚野？"},{"pid":"9e9367b73fd8532032fa5fd3a85fd2fcdca50a69","tid":1935553,"uid":205749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"而家咪屌緊偷走嗰d囉<br />\n係咪唔屌得呀<br />\n<br />\n你真係香港人嘅話<br />\n絕對有權返香港享受成果<br />\n不會唔好咁撚缺德 去破壞守咗兩個月嘅香港<br />\n咁嘅話 你同支那種有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n再者 大家驚都好正常啫<br />\n咁有冇人體諒下守住香港嘅人呀？"},{"pid":"d7c59028e90559ea28fd8834b9d98d97ea83b5dd","tid":1935553,"uid":205749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb8728916369d3053f68033258b63b4bbae6387","tid":1935553,"uid":168669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"返黎做咩撚野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T17:58:13.000Z","msg":"避難囉 仲可以做乜嘢"}]}